import time

def process_data(mem_data):
    data_time = []
    mem_percent = []
    for doc in mem_data:
        unix_time = doc['timestamp']
        times = time.localtime(unix_time)
        dt = time.strftime('%m%d-%H:%M', times)
        data_time.append(dt)
        m_percent = doc['mem']['percent']
        mem_percent.append(m_percent)
    data = {'': data_time, 'mem_percent': mem_percent}
    return data
